@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hfefxl(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.cos(v0 + 0.92) * 0.95))
    v1 = tmp
    v2 = (tmp * (tmp - wp.cos(tmp + 0.27)))
    v0 = 0.60
    tmp = (v0 * 0.52)
    v0 = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.99) + (v2 + 0.37 + v1 + 0.39)) * wp.exp(0.75))
    tmp = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.00 * v1 + 0.98)) + ((tmp + 0.99 / tmp + 0.22) * (tmp + 0.83 / tmp + 0.65)))
    v1 = (wp.sin(tmp) * ((v0 + 0.61 / tmp + 0.96) + wp.cos(tmp + 0.43)))
    data[tid] = v0
